# Remember Learning

When the user asks to remember, learn, save this, 记住, 学习, or 保存经验, save one reusable learning to:

`/home/tan/agent-learning/learnings/`

Rules:

- Write the learning note in Chinese.
- Use the existing `learnings/` folder only.
- Do not create extra folders like `patterns/`, `notes/`, or `skills/`.
- Do not store secrets or raw conversation dumps.
- Use the canonical helper script:

```bash
node /home/tan/agent-learning/.agents/skills/remember/scripts/save-learning.mjs \
  --title "{topic}" \
  --agent "Cursor Agent <cursor-agent@cursor.com>" \
  --commit
```

After saving, report the saved file path and commit hash.
